Taylor v. Tinsley, Warden; Bell v. Maryland; and Costello v. Klinger, Superintendent, Department of Corrections, California Men's Colony.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as petitions for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
